  "detailed_description": "<strong>Froggo Swing 'n Grapple</strong> is a side-scrolling platformer game about a little frog on an adventure to find his pet rock, Jotao.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743930/extras/0a184d7456f60bf5e80e2a8087b50376.poster.avif?t=1753884293\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743930/extras/0a184d7456f60bf5e80e2a8087b50376.webm?t=1753884293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743930/extras/0a184d7456f60bf5e80e2a8087b50376.mp4?t=1753884293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Swing 'n grapple across the stages using Froggo's powerful and sticky tongue!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743930/extras/5f1391485027d1824b315709d9327196.poster.avif?t=1753884293\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743930/extras/5f1391485027d1824b315709d9327196.webm?t=1753884293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743930/extras/5f1391485027d1824b315709d9327196.mp4?t=1753884293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Interact with different parts of the stages to progress through the levels!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743930/extras/822f0dea8a32132989dcb83d72e69672.poster.avif?t=1753884293\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743930/extras/822f0dea8a32132989dcb83d72e69672.webm?t=1753884293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743930/extras/822f0dea8a32132989dcb83d72e69672.mp4?t=1753884293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Git gud and take advantage of your grappling skills!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fun side-scrolling action with a twist<br></li><li>An adventure consists of 8 different stages, each introduces unique theming and stage elements.<br></li><li>Freely Swing 'n Grapple anywhere! Complete the stages in however way you see fit!<br></li><li>Optional secret areas are hidden within all the stages. Can you find them all?<br></li><li>Shoes shops allows you to buy shoes that power up your platforming ability!</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Froggo Swing 'n Grapple</strong> is a side-scrolling platformer game about a little frog on an adventure to find his pet rock, Jotao.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743930/extras/0a184d7456f60bf5e80e2a8087b50376.poster.avif?t=1753884293\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743930/extras/0a184d7456f60bf5e80e2a8087b50376.webm?t=1753884293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743930/extras/0a184d7456f60bf5e80e2a8087b50376.mp4?t=1753884293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Swing 'n grapple across the stages using Froggo's powerful and sticky tongue!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743930/extras/5f1391485027d1824b315709d9327196.poster.avif?t=1753884293\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743930/extras/5f1391485027d1824b315709d9327196.webm?t=1753884293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743930/extras/5f1391485027d1824b315709d9327196.mp4?t=1753884293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Interact with different parts of the stages to progress through the levels!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743930/extras/822f0dea8a32132989dcb83d72e69672.poster.avif?t=1753884293\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743930/extras/822f0dea8a32132989dcb83d72e69672.webm?t=1753884293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743930/extras/822f0dea8a32132989dcb83d72e69672.mp4?t=1753884293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Git gud and take advantage of your grappling skills!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fun side-scrolling action with a twist<br></li><li>An adventure consists of 8 different stages, each introduces unique theming and stage elements.<br></li><li>Freely Swing 'n Grapple anywhere! Complete the stages in however way you see fit!<br></li><li>Optional secret areas are hidden within all the stages. Can you find them all?<br></li><li>Shoes shops allows you to buy shoes that power up your platforming ability!</li></ul>",
